          "alt": "IMG_70541"
        }}></img></a></p>
    <p>{`After getting our fill of the area, and after Laura discovered some very decadent ice cream flavors to sample, we caught a bus down to the fishing village of Tai O. This village, built on stilts over the water is supposed to be more similar to what Hong Kong historically looked like prior to being westernized by the British. Spotted fishing communities among the islands. The area was pretty, and reminded us of Morro Bay back at home. With narrow shop-lined walkways we wandered the ‘streets’ of Tai O, until we had enough of all the dried smells.`}</p>
    <p><a parentName="p" {...{
